A cyberpunk cityscape at night where towering government buildings made of transparent glass and neon-lit circuitry rise from murky shadows below. Digital streams of data flow visibly through the glass walls like glowing rivers, while at street level, shadowy figures in traditional clothing reach upward toward the pristine digital towers. The contrast between the clean, luminous upper levels with their orderly data streams and the chaotic, fog-shrouded streets below creates a stark visual divide. Southeast Asian architectural elements blend with futuristic holographic interfaces floating in the air. Rain falls through beams of magenta and cyan light, reflecting off wet streets where old paper documents dissolve into digital particles rising toward the towers above.
